name: Version 2.2.3
body:
* Fix panic when pushing a message without config
* Allow passing the application token via the environment variable: `GOTIFY_TOKEN`
* Update dependencies

name: Version 2.1.0
body:
* Evaluate `\n` and `\t` in messages (can be disabled via `--disable-unescape-backslash`) (#18)
* Added watch command (#20)
* Fixed ignored user config (#21)

name: Version 2.0.0
body:
* Update to go-api-client v2.0.4 (https://github.com/gotify/cli/pull/16)
* Added `contentType` flag to `push` command (https://github.com/gotify/cli/pull/16)
  See https://gotify.net/docs/msgextras#client-display

name: Version 1.2.2
body: * Add i386 build target (#11 fixed in #12)
